information: SARL PHELIN MULTI-SERVICES is active across a range of market sectors. We are teak growers and we sell raw teak timber (approximately 27 years old) for the manufacture of all types of furniture, luxury car and aircraft dashboards, etc. We have 3, 600 hectares of teak timber available to us and we sell all over the world. We are also producers and growers of quality ginger and Shea butter. We work with cosmetics companies, wholesalers, resellers, etc., in Europe and internationally. All our products are made at our premises in western Ivory Coast. For any requests, please contact us by email.
